&lt;h2 id="part-1"&gt;Part 1&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Implement a &lt;a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/PRNG"&gt;PRNG&lt;/a&gt; with the following update function:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Multiply by 64, xor with the previous value, &lt;a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/modulo"&gt;modulo&lt;/a&gt; 16777216&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Divide by 32, xor with the previous value (from step 1), modulo 16777216&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Multiply by 2048, xor with the previous value (from step 2), module 16777216&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For each of a series of seeds, sum the 2000th generated number.&lt;/p&gt;
